nginx open source - Is onen source version of NGINX with limited support and less features
nginx plus - is enterprised edition of software with rich functionality 

To check difference between nging and nginx plus : https://www.nginx.com/products/nginx/compare-models/

In this course we will learn about Nginx open source and how we can use it in our project.

- Installation : https://docs.nginx.com/nginx/admin-guide/installing-nginx/installing-nginx-open-source/
    -  Install from prebuilt packages
    -  Compile from source 

- Deploying NGINX with docker : https://docs.nginx.com/nginx/admin-guide/installing-nginx/installing-nginx-docker/


